{"tid":138772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北京政協晉身港大管理層 內地學者蔡洪濱掌經濟及工管學院","createTime":"2017-03-01T00:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-01T00:40:59.000Z","uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"16ef8de7ea73c0ffd2af9215b094fd07ad9a0690","tid":138772,"uid":73262,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:36:40.000Z","msg":"港大正式委任前北京大學光華管理學院院長、身兼江西省全國人大及北京市政協的內地學者蔡洪濱，接任港大經濟及工商管理學院院長，蔡將於今年7月1日上任，任期為5年。早前有傳蔡為接任新院長的唯一候選人。<br />\n<br />\n港大今日傍晚舉行校委會會議，議程包括討論經濟及工商管理學院新院長任命。根據港大學生刊物《學苑》網上報道，今日下午5時40分，校長馬斐森向大學師生發電郵，宣佈校委會已正式委任蔡洪濱。<br />\n<br />\n馬斐森於電郵中指，蔡洪濱擔任北大光華管理學院院長7年，具充足的管理、領導經驗，又指蔡在博奕論、中國經濟及企業金融等範疇是享負盛名的學者，相信蔡可帶領學院更進一步。<br />\n<br />\n早前傳出北大學者蔡洪濱將接替台灣學者張介，成為港大經濟及工商管理學院院長，蔡更是唯一一名新院長候選人。蔡洪濱將成為首位晉身港大高層的內地學者，但未知他會否在上任前辭去人大代表、政協等職務。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56367232&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170228\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56367232%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170228&d=RNMQoofY58y8BAaKNkwZNk%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=5cbe6ad9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D56367232%26category_guid%3D6996647%26category%3Dinstant%26issue%3D20170228&h=3fd1a62b\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=56367232&amp;category_guid=6996647&amp;category=instant&amp;issue=20170228</a>"},{"pid":"bc79b96db2a7467e7473a266904fff0967f95ae1","tid":138772,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"26761daff05a3bb43f9b319cd3924320c2528cab","tid":138772,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:40:29.000Z","msg":"佢D英文得唔得嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95067c111251d2cc2597de3bd249f3c238202fbb","tid":138772,"uid":31405,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T00:40:59.000Z","msg":"又侵佔一個位了"}]}